**Verification:**

```
| Record   | Physical Offset                   | Decoded Ptr | Formula Check                |
| -------- | --------------------------------- | ----------- | ---------------------------- |
| AACCOUNT | 0x0000c006 (page 12, offset 6)    | 0x00003006  | 12 * 0x400 + 6 = 0x3006 ✅    |
| ATOP     | 0x000088e4 (page 8, offset 0x8e4) | 0x000078e4  | 8 * 0x400 + 0x8e4 = 0x78e4 ✅ |
```
**To encode for the exporter:**

```
uint32_t encodePtr(uint32_t physicalOffset, uint32_t pageLength) {
    uint32_t page = physicalOffset / pageLength;
    uint32_t offset = physicalOffset % pageLength;
    return (page * 0x400) + offset;
}
```
